# MoodDic Mobile

Expo SDK 57 client for MoodDic. API lives in `moodjournal` on GitHub.

- Mood check-ins sync via `/mood` (`services/moodService.ts`) — do not keep new flows local-only.
- Use Expo Router navigation helpers — never import `@react-navigation/*` in app code.
- Prefer `npm start` (LAN) or `npm run start:offline` for device work; install with `--legacy-peer-deps`.
- Resolve API URL via `config/appConfig.ts` / `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` (port 8080).
- Keep the gamified green brand unless asked otherwise. No project-scoped MCP required.
